     2	
     3	## Bottom line
     4	
     5	This chain is attacking a real bottleneck, but it is too eager to upgrade an
     6	epistemic gap into a mathematical separation theorem. The repository already
     7	records three damaging facts: Step 6 froze `G_tmpl` and `G_leak` as screening
     8	objects rather than implication theorems, Step 7 froze downstream work to the
     9	single witness `F_SS(1/12)` on one canonical ledger, and Step 8 stopped at
    10	exact non-isolability because no finite exact support-level closure ledger is
