   175	
   176	### Step 5 - Decide The Downstream Consequence For Mission Objects
   177	
   178	This step is mostly predetermined by the earlier record.
   179	
   180	- If Step 8 already says no finite exact closure object is frozen, then the
   181	  default downstream consequence is already plain: `G_tmpl` and `G_leak` remain
   182	  screening tools, not closure theorems.
